   LOCAL HARDENING (AAW): User-controllable strings injected into JSON-LD have
   been wrapped with the `| json` filter to prevent JSON-context XSS via
   unescaped quotes / backslashes in product, article, author, page, and
   collection data. Do not revert when the upstream app updates; re-apply this
   patch on top of the new version, or upstream may re-introduce the issue.
